data.description: Absolutely stunning 4-bed 3-bath pool home in the desirable SW Cape Coral neighborhood. Boasting over 3300 sq. ft of living space, this spacious home is an entertainer's dream. Enjoy the elegance of a formal dining room and a versatile den that can be transformed into your ideal space. The large pantry and butler's pantry make meal prep a breeze, and the loft area adds an extra dimension of versatility to this home.  Don't let this opportunity pass you by - make this piece of paradise your own today!
